<plot>Worms kills, that's what he does. He tries to convince himself that each one is the last as he moves from city to city, leaving a trail of bloody corpses, but he knows better. The memory of each death slowly eats away at his soul, but he cannot stop. Alone in his seedy hotel room, he picks up his phone and begins to dial. Taking his call inexperienced recruit Sarah Farren is totally unprepared for her first encounter with true evil. The Police have been hunting him but have thus far failed. She slowly discovers that Worms wishes for the violence to end. Out of her depth but trying to make a difference, she fails to see the genuine horrifying motive behind Worms astonishing confession.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?661252</url></doc>
